OL,3,CBirmingham has first Lib Dem council
OL,4,Cleader after coalition vote
OL,6,FCouncillors have chosen Roger Harmer
OL,7,Fas the new leader of Birmingham City
OL,8,FCouncil - confirming an unusual power-
OL,9,Fsharing arrangement between the
OL,10,FLiberal Democrats and Greens.
OL,12,FThe deal, described by coalition
OL,13,Ffigures as a form of "joint
OL,14,Fleadership", will see the two parties
OL,15,Feffectively share control of the
OL,16,Fcouncil, despite only one person
OL,17,Fformally being able to hold the title
OL,18,Fof leader at any one time.
OL,26,@uD@VOUvD@KO]
