OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780845083
OL,3,CBirmingham has first Lib Dem council
OL,4,Cleader after coalition vote
OL,6,FDespite his party only winning 12
OL,7,Fseats, Roger Harmer, leader of the
OL,8,FLiberal Democrat group, will take the
OL,9,Frole first - becoming the first
OL,10,FLiberal Democrat to lead the council.
OL,12,FUnder the agreement, Green group
OL,13,Fleader Julien Pritchard is expected to
OL,14,Fbecome leader at a later stage - after
OL,15,Fhis party won 19 seats.
OL,17,FThe coalition - made up of the Greens,
OL,18,FLiberal Democrats and Better
OL,19,FBirmingham Independents - does not
OL,20,Fcommand an outright majority in the
OL,21,Fcouncil chamber.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
