FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780845083
OL,3,CBirmingham has first Lib Dem council
OL,4,Cleader after coalition vote
OL,6,FAlong with a grouping of independents,
OL,7,Fthey have 40 councillors - short of
OL,8,Fthe 51 needed for a majority.
OL,10,FSenior figures involved in the
OL,11,Fagreement believe there is enough
OL,12,Fcommon ground across parties to allow
OL,13,Fthe administration to function.
OL,15,FSupporters have said the arrangement
OL,16,Freflects the fragmented political
OL,17,Fmakeup of the council following May's
OL,18,Flocal elections.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
