PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780845083
OL,3,CBirmingham has first Lib Dem council
OL,4,Cleader after coalition vote
OL,6,FReform UK, who have 23 seats, had
OL,7,Fcriticised the proposal ahead of the
OL,8,Fvote, describing it as "musical
OL,9,Fchairs" leadership.
OL,11,FLabour previously warned against "a
OL,12,Fconstantly rotating cast of leaders",
OL,13,Fsaying Birmingham residents needed
OL,14,Fstability at a difficult time for the
OL,15,Fauthority.
OL,17,FThe new administration now inherits a
OL,18,Fseries of major challenges - including
OL,19,Fthe ongoing bin strike, the council's
OL,20,Ffinancial recovery and long-running
OL,21,Fequal pay liabilities.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
